[30;1m112 | [0m[35m# How many of the total rows need to be downloaded already for us to skip[0m

[30;1m114 | [0m[35m#[0m

[30;1m116 | [0m[35m# remaining results, it's faster to use the BQ Storage Read API to download[0m
[30;1m117 | [0m[35m# the results than use jobs.getQueryResults. Since we don't have a good way to[0m
[30;1m118 | [0m[35m# know the remaining bytes, we estimate by remaining number of rows.[0m
